summary: This mod adds 5 or 6 spell tomes into arcadias couldron these spells are lightning storm bound bow lightning strike or something like that and 3 other spells.
descriptionHtml: This is my second mod i have basically added 5 of my favorite spells into arcadias couldron interier. so go to whiterun and go in arcadias couldron look on the counter and there will be 5 or 6 spell tomes for you to take. Please enjoy this mod it\'s probably more successful then the skyforge mod i made.
